OL,3,C'Racism normalised' say Teesside
OL,4,CMuslims after riots in Hartlepool
OL,6,FKris Jepson's met Muslims in
OL,7,FMiddlesbrough who are now scared to
OL,8,Fleave their own home, following riots
OL,9,Fin Hartlepool.
OL,11,FThe Muslim community in Middlesbrough
OL,12,Fis questioning how safe they are
OL,13,Ffollowing a night of riots in nearby
OL,14,FHartlepool.
OL,16,FFar-right protestors gathered in the
OL,17,Ftown on Wednesday 31 July, with the
OL,18,Fscenes descending into violence and
OL,19,Fdisorder.
