OL,6,FHe told ITV News there has been a rise
OL,7,Fin tensions since the 7 October Hamas
OL,8,Fattack on Israel, adding: "The anti-
OL,9,FMuslim, the anti-Pakistani comments
OL,10,Fthat you hear, racist abuse, it almost
OL,11,Ffeels like we're back to those dark
OL,12,Fdays of the 80s and 90s, where racism
OL,13,Fis now normalised again, and
OL,14,Fespecially towards Muslims.
OL,16,F"Not just from the kind of content
OL,17,Fthat we see online, but actual on-the-
OL,18,Fstreet racial abuse. Be that verbal or
OL,19,Fphysical, it is manifesting more and
OL,20,Fmore, right across the North East and
OL,21,Fespecially in Teesside."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
