OL,6,FWhen asked how it can be dealt with,
OL,7,Fhe added: "As much as there is some
OL,8,Ffantastic work taking place, it does
OL,9,Fseem to be quite tokenistic, you know,
OL,10,Falmost a tick box exercise.
OL,12,F"Everyone needs to do more. We need to
OL,13,Fbe more sincere, we need to have those
OL,14,Fconversations, but ultimately, it's
OL,15,Fgoing to be a grassroots movement that
OL,16,Fwill change the situation that we find
OL,17,Fourselves in."
