OL,6,FWorshippers at the Jamia Masjid Al-
OL,7,FMadina Mosque in the town were offered
OL,8,Freassurance by the Imam, who told them
OL,9,Fto be careful when attending the
OL,10,FMosque. Some of the Muslim elders
OL,11,Fdecided to pray at home.
OL,13,FNajabat Ramzan, from the Mosque, told
OL,14,FITV News: "People in the community are
OL,15,Fscared and afraid.
OL,17,F"I mean my own wife didn't want to go
OL,18,Fto town this morning with a little
OL,19,Fkid, because she's afraid. In
OL,20,FMiddlesbrough and Teesside we always
OL,21,Fgot on well with each other.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
