OL,6,F"There's been no issues and really,
OL,7,Fit's a united community, but it makes
OL,8,Fme feel really sad and it makes you
OL,9,Fthink, how safe are we?"
OL,11,FWhy did it happen in Hartlepool?
OL,13,FWith the recent murder of a pensioner
OL,14,Fby an asylum seeker in Hartlepool, the
OL,15,Fformer MP claiming she wanted illegal
OL,16,Fasylum seekers "expelled", and the
OL,17,Frise of Reform in the general
OL,18,Felection, were these divisions just
OL,19,Fsimmering?
