OL,6,FDuring the disorder, social media
OL,7,Fvideos were posted in which rioters
OL,8,Fchanted the name "Tommy Robinson" as
OL,9,Fthey smashed down windows and doors of
OL,10,Fproperties.
OL,12,FRobinson, whose real name is Stephen
OL,13,FYaxley-Lennon, is currently abroad,
OL,14,Fevading an arrest warrant, but he took
OL,15,Fto social media on Wednesday night to
OL,16,Fpost about events in Hartlepool.
