OL,6,FIn one post he wrote: "As disorder
OL,7,Fspreads to Hartlepool, don't say I
OL,8,Fdidn't warn you. They sent out the
OL,9,Fmessage that riots work over the last
OL,10,Ffew weeks."
OL,12,FRobinson is the co-founder of the now
OL,13,Fdefunct English Defence League (EDL),
OL,14,Fa far right Islamophobic group.
OL,16,FDr Gavin Hart, Liverpool Hope
OL,17,FUniversity criminologist and expert in
OL,18,Fthe far-right, told ITV News we have
OL,19,Fseen far-right groups like the EDL and
OL,20,FBritain First "building over the last
OL,21,Fdecade".
